ates\u202fC** or **D** that have not yet been disclosed.\nGiven the present evidence, **Candidate\u202fB remains the strongest overall choice** for a long\u2011distance pilot position, provided that his communication issues can be addressed through training or crew\u2011resource\u2011management interventions.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
